entry.title: bracke/MakeLink
entry.summary: MakeLink creates an 'empty' application which points to another application (the target) of your choice. Double clicking on the new application will run the target application, selecting 'Help' in the filer menu will open the help of the target application. NOTE: This is a RISC OS app.
